going fast in the code signal. But it was just a

02:09.548 --> 02:14.897
small town, country town. It's grown up into large 
apartments around. I had a sister that

02:21.127 --> 02:27.538
was one of the wanderers of the family. went up to 
the North Coast, North Cape, and she got to be a

02:28.683 --> 02:34.148
school teacher. And she taught down the Panama 
Canal, and she taught up in a hospital up in New York

02:35.410 --> 02:44.739
State. She was a physical education teacher, and 
