boy, appendicitis. Didn't know much about

03:10.182 --> 03:12.486
appendicitis in those days. And so we grew up and 
I've lost track of most of the people. There's one

03:22.822 --> 03:23.783
boy that We bought a second-hand canoe and kept it 
down in Jamaica Bay, close to one of the present

03:24.792 --> 03:30.539
airports.

03:33.663 --> 03:35.185
We sailed around Long Island. In a canoe? Yeah, 
there's a string of, just like down in Padre

03:37.387 --> 03:48.761
Island, there's a string of islands along the 
ocean shore, and then you've got the Long Island

03:37.387 --> 03:48.761
Sound on the inside. So it's... It's an inland 
waterway. It's an inland waterway, yeah. That

03:57.057 --> 03:58.439
sounds like a fascinating experience. Well, it's 
